OL,4,CPalace manager
OL,6,FRoy Hodgson has stepped down from his
OL,7,Fpost as Crystal Palace manager, the
OL,8,Fclub have announced.
OL,10,FThe announcement was made hours before
OL,11,Ftheir Premier League meeting with
OL,12,FEverton on Monday.
OL,14,FA club statement also confirmed the 76-
OL,15,Fyear-old, on Thursday, was "out of
OL,16,Fhospital and doing well".
