OL,6,FHodgson's right-hand man Ray Lewington
OL,7,Fand assistant manager Paddy McCarthy
OL,8,Fwill lead the team on Monday at
OL,9,FGoodison Park, with the Eagles just
OL,10,Ffive points clear of their opponents
OL,11,Fwho are in the relegation zone.
OL,13,FHodgson, in a statement released by
OL,14,Fthe club, said: "This club is very
OL,15,Fspecial and means so much to me and
OL,16,Fhas played a big part in my
OL,17,Ffootballing life.
