OL,3,CRoy Hodgson steps down as Crystal
OL,4,CPalace manager
OL,6,F"I have fully enjoyed my time here
OL,7,Facross six seasons, as it has given me
OL,8,Fthe chance to work with top class
OL,9,Fplayers and staff doing what I love
OL,10,Fevery day."
OL,12,FThe statement added: "However, I
OL,13,Funderstand, given recent
OL,14,Fcircumstances, it may be prudent at
OL,15,Fthis time for the club to plan ahead,
OL,16,Fand therefore I have taken the
OL,17,Fdecision to step aside so that the
OL,18,Fclub can bring forward their plans for
OL,19,Fa new manager, as intended for this
OL,20,Fsummer.
