OL,6,FPalace sit 15th in the top flight,
OL,7,Ffive points above the relegation zone,
OL,8,Fahead of the upcoming clash with
OL,9,FEverton.
OL,11,FHodgson took charge of his 200th match
OL,12,Fas Eagles manager last Monday when his
OL,13,Fside were beaten 3-1 at Selhurst Park
OL,14,Fby Chelsea.
OL,16,FPalace have won just six of 24 league
OL,17,Ffixtures this term, with only three of
OL,18,Fthose victories coming since a 1-0
OL,19,Fsuccess at Manchester United in
OL,20,FSeptember.
